Function PopByCoef(Pop,Coef)
wave Pop, Coef


variable ii, points, traces

points=DimSize(Pop,0)
traces=NumPnts(Coef)
 
Duplicate /o pop, Results
Redimension /n=(-1,traces) Results

for (ii=0;ii<traces;ii+=1)

		results[][ii]=Pop[p][Coef[ii]]
		
endfor

end

